imit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk5ODAy/p90599015_highres_bmw-motorrad-concept.jpg 256w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_384,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk5ODAy/p90599015_highres_bmw-motorrad-concept.jpg 384w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_640,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk5ODAy/p90599015_highres_bmw-motorrad-concept.jpg 640w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_750,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk5ODAy/p90599015_highres_bmw-motorrad-concept.jpg 750w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_828,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk5ODAy/p90599015_highres_bmw-motorrad-concept.jpg 828w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1080,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk5ODAy/p90599015_highres_bmw-motorrad-concept.jpg 1080w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1200,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk5ODAy/p90599015_highres_bmw-motorrad-concept.jpg 1200w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1920,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk5ODAy/p90599015_highres_bmw-motorrad-concept.jpg 1920w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_2048,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk5ODAy/p90599015_highres_bmw-motorrad-concept.jpg 2048w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_3840,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk5ODAy/p90599015_highres_bmw-motorrad-concept.jpg 3840w\" src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_3840,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk5ODAy/p90599015_highres_bmw-motorrad-concept.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/article\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"as-fast-as-it-is-pretty\"\u003eAs fast as it is pretty\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp data-wp-block=\"{\u0026#34;dropCap\u0026#34;:false}\" data-wp-block-name=\"core/paragraph\"\u003eAll of this isn’t to say that the \u003ca href=\"https://www.autoblog.com/aston-martin/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eAston Martin\u003c/a\u003e Palm Beach Edition DB12 Volante is all show and no go. Underneath that gorgeous, long hood is a twin-turbocharged 4.0-liter V8 making 671 horsepower through an 8-speed ZF automatic transmission. Aston estimates that the DB12 can sprint from zero to 60 mph in 3.4 seconds and has a top speed of 202 mph, so we’d hold on to our hats if we were you. Yes, we know, the V12 of the DB11 is gone, but hey, at least it’s not electric. Aston did not reveal a pricing figure for the bespoke one-off, nor who commissioned it, but given that the regular DB12 Volante starts at $271,825, we’d rather not know its price tag.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Aston Martin DB12 Palm Beach Edition\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"5986\" height=\"3991\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" sizes=\"(min-width: 750px) 750px, calc(100vw - 60px)\" srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_16,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAxMTkz/aston-martin-db12-volante-palm-beach-edition-10.jpg 16w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_32,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAxMTkz/aston-martin-db12-volante-palm-beach-edition-10.jpg 32w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_48,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAxMTkz/aston-martin-db12-volante-palm-beach-edition-10.jpg 48w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_64,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAxMTkz/aston-martin-db12-volante-palm-beach-edition-10.jpg 64w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_96,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAxMTkz/aston-martin-db12-volante-palm-beach-edition-10.jpg 96w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_128,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAxMTkz/aston-martin-db12-volante-palm-beach-edition-10.jpg 128w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_256,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAxMTkz/aston-martin-db12-volante-palm-beach-edition-10.jpg 256w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_384,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAxMTkz/aston-martin-db12-volante-palm-beach-edition-10.jpg 384w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_640,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAxMTkz/aston-martin-db12-volante-palm-beach-edition-10.jpg 640w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_750,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAxMTkz/aston-martin-db12-volante-palm-beach-edition-10.jpg 750w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_828,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAxMTkz/aston-martin-db12-volante-palm-beach-edition-10.jpg 828w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1080,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAxMTkz/aston-martin-db12-volante-palm-beach-edition-10.jpg 1080w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1200,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAxMTkz/aston-martin-db12-volante-palm-beach-edition-10.jpg 1200w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1920,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAxMTkz/aston-martin-db12-volante-palm-beach-edition-10.jpg 1920w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_2048,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAxMTkz/aston-martin-db12-volante-palm-beach-edition-10.jpg 2048w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_3840,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAxMTkz/aston-martin-db12-volante-palm-beach-edition-10.jpg 3840w\" src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_3840,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAxMTkz/aston-martin-db12-volante-palm-beach-edition-10.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"final-thoughts\"\u003eFinal thoughts\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp data-wp-block=\"{\u0026#34;dropCap\u0026#34;:false}\" data-wp-block-name=\"core/paragraph\"\u003eIt’s always fun seeing what automakers’ bespoke divisions can create for their most distinguished clients. If you want the most opulent vehicle that money can buy, you’ll likely go to \u003ca href=\"https://www.autoblog.com/rolls-royce/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eRolls-Royce\u003c/a\u003e’s bespoke department. If you want a sports car with a color that pops, \u003ca href=\"https://www.autoblog.com/porsche/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ePorsche\u003c/a\u003e’s Paint-to-Sample program would likely be pretty high on that list. \u003ca href=\"https://www.autoblog.com/aston-martin/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eAston Martin\u003c/a\u003e’s Q department doesn’t often make headlines, but if they keep making cars like the Palm Beach Edition DB12 Volante, we can see how that would easily change.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003csection\u003e\u003carticle\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca aria-label=\"View post: Best and Worst Gear Shift Knobs in 2025\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"https://www.autoblog.com/features/best-and-worst-gear-shift-knobs-2025\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Porsche 911 Carrera T\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(min-width: 790px) 375px, (min-width: 768px) calc(50vw - 24px), calc(100vw - 24px)\" srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_16,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk5NjY3/lugano_blue_911_carrera_t_cabriolet_035__sim2117.jpg 16w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_32,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk5NjY3/lugano_blue_911_carrera_t_cabriolet_035__sim2117.jpg 32w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_48,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk5NjY3/lugano_blue_911_carrera_t_cabriolet_035__sim2117.jpg 48w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_64,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk5NjY3/lugano_blue_911_carrera_t_cabriolet_035__sim2117.jpg 64w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_96,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk5NjY3/lugano_blue_911_carrera_t_cabriolet_035__sim2117.jpg 96w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_128,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk5NjY3/lugano_blue_911_carrera_t_cabriolet_035__sim2117.jpg 128w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_256,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk5NjY3/lugano_blue_911_carrera_t_cabriolet_035__sim2117.jpg 256w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_384,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk5NjY3/lugano_blue_911_carrera_t_cabriolet_035__sim2117.jpg 384w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_640,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk5NjY3/lugano_blue_911_carrera_t_cabriolet_035__sim2117.jpg 640w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_750,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk5NjY3/luga